Title: Collaborators
Plot: Tyrol participates in the Circle, a secret tribunal on Galactica that tries and convicts in absentia those accused of collaborating with the Cylons during the Occupation.The death sentences--administered without the knowledge of Roslin or Adama--begin to weigh on Tyrol's conscience.Baltar faces a similar jury among the Cylons, who must decide whether he is allowed to stay with them.
ParentalRatingReason: M Violence,sexual references and offensive language
GuestStars: Winston Rekert, Alisen Down, Alessandro Juliani
